h1. properties

h2. 目的 {hidden}Purpose{hidden}

Allows access to the domain class properties as a Map and is typically used for [Data Binding|guide:dataBinding] to perform type conversions allowing properties to be set from request parameters or other Maps.

h2. 使用例 {hidden}Examples{hidden}

{code:java}
def b = new Book(title: "The Shining")
b.properties = params
b.save()
{code}
